\c 23
\s Imwe mirairo
\p
\v 1 Usamutsa shoko renhema. Usaisa ruoko rwako pamwe newakaipa kuti uve chapupu chisakarurama.
\p
\v 2 Usatevera vazhinji pane zvakaipa. Uye usapupura pamhosva nevazhinji kuti utsause.
\p
\v 3 Nemurombo usamunzwira ngoni pamhosva yake.
\p
\v 4 Kana ukasangana nenzombe yemuvengi wako kana mbongoro yake yakarasika, zvirokwazvo uchaidzosera kwaari.
\v 5 Kana ukaona mbongoro yeanokuvenga irere pasi pemutoro wayo, ungarega kuinunura here? Zvirokwazvo uchanunura iyo naiye.
\p
\v 6 Usatsausa mutongo wemurombo wako pamhosva yake.
\v 7 Iva kure nenyaya yenhema, uye asina mhosva newakarurama usauraya, nokuti handingaruramisiri wakaipa.
\p
\v 8 Uye usatora fufuro, nokuti fufuro inopofumadza vanoona, nekutsausa mashoko evakarurama.
\p
\v 9 Uye usadzvinyirira mutorwa, nokuti imwi munoziva moyo wemutorwa, zvamakange muri vatorwa munyika yeEgipita.
\p
\v 10 Zvino makore matanhatu uchadzvara munda wako, uye uunganidze zvibereko zvawo.
\v 11 Asi nerechinomwe uchauzorodza nekuurega urare, kuti varombo verudzi rwako vadye, nezvavanosiya mhuka dzesango dzichadya. Saizvozvo uite nemunda wako wemizambiringa nemunda wako \add we\add*miorivhi.
\v 12 Mazuva matanhatu uchaita mabasa rako, uye nezuva rechinomwe uchazorora, kuti nzombe yako nembongoro yako zvizorore, nemwanakomana wemurandakadzi wako nemutorwa vambofema.
\v 13 Zvino pazvinhu zvese zvandakakuudzai muzvichenjerere; uye musareva zita revamwe vamwari; Hazvinganzwikwi kubva mumuromo wako.
\p
\v 14 Katatu pagore uchandichengetedzera mutambo.
\v 15 Uchachengetedza mutambo wechingwa chisina kuviriswa; uchadya chingwa chisina kuviriswa mazuva manomwe sezvandakakuraira, panguva yakatarwa yemwedzi Abhibhi; (nokuti nawo wakabuda muEgipita); zvino havangaonekwi pamberi pangu vasina chavakabata.
\v 16 Uye mutambo wekukohwa, zvibereko zvekutanga zvemabasa ako, zvawakadzvara mumunda; uye mutambo wekuunganidza pakupera kwegore, kana waunganidza zvemabasa ako pamunda.
\v 17 Katatu pagore vanhurume venyu vese vachaonekwa pamberi paShe Jehovha.
\p
\v 18 Hauchabairi ropa rechibairo changu pamwe chete nechingwa chakaviriswa; nemafuta emutambo wangu haachagari kusvika kwaedza.
\v 19 Chekutanga \add pakunaka\add* chezvibereko zvemunda wako zvekutanga uchauisa muimba yaJehovha Mwari wako. Usabika mbudzana mumukaka wamai vayo.
\p
\v 20 Tarira, ndinotuma Mutumwa pamberi pako kukuchengeta panzira, nekukuisa munzvimbo yandakagadzirira.
\v 21 Chenjerera pamberi pake, uye teerera inzwi rake, usamutsamwisa, nokuti haangakanganwiri kudarika kwako, nokuti zita rangu riri mukati maari.
\v 22 Asi kana ukateerera zvirokwazvo inzwi rake, nekuita zvese zvandinotaura, ipapo ndichava muvengi wevavengi vako, nemudzivisi wevadzivisi vako.
\v 23 Nokuti Mutumwa wangu achafamba mberi kwako, akuuyise kuVaAmori, neVaHeti, neVaPerezi, neVaKenani, neVaHivhi, neVaJebhusi. Uye ndichavaparadza.
\v 24 Usapfugamira vamwari vavo, kana kuvashumira, kana kuita semabasa avo; asi uchavabvumbura zvekuvabvumbura, nekuputsanya-putsanya shongwe dzavo zvifananidzo.
\v 25 Zvino muchashumira Jehovha Mwari wenyu, uye acharopafadza kudya kwenyu nemvura yenyu; neni ndichabvisa urwere pakati penyu.
\p
\v 26 Hakungavi nechinosvodza, kana chisingabereki panyika yako. Ndichazadzisa mazuva ako.
\p
\v 27 Ndichatuma kutyisa kwangu pamberi pako, nekukanganisa vanhu vese vauchasvika kwavari, nekufuratidza vavengi vako vese.
\v 28 Ndichatuma mago pamberi pako achadzinga VaHivhi, VaKenani, neVaHeti kubva pamberi pako.
\v 29 Handingavadzingi kubva pamberi pako mugore rimwe, zvimwe nyika ingava dongo, nezvikara zvesango zvikuwandire.
\v 30 Zvishoma nezvishoma ndichavadzinga kubva pamberi pako, kusvikira mawanda mugare nhaka yenyika.
\v 31 Zvino ndichaisa miganhu yako kubva paGungwa Dzvuku kusvikawo kuGungwa reVaFirisitia, nekubva kurenje kusvika kuRwizi, nokuti ndichapa vagari venyika muruoko rwako zvino uchavadzinga pamberi pako.
\v 32 Haungaiti sungano navo kana nevamwari vavo.
\v 33 Havangagari munyika yako, zvimwe vangakuita unditadzire, nokuti kana ukashumira vamwari vavo, zvirokwazvo uchava musungo kwauri.
